data.description:
Colorado's natural beauty surrounds this charming custom home tucked away in beautiful Mountain Shadows.  Situated on a spectacular .39 acre private lot with scrub oak, aspen trees, flat lawn area, side patio, mountain and city views.  Stucco and stone adorn this 2 story home with covered front porch overlooking the city and surrounding mountains.  From the moment you enter the beautiful hand crafted custom arched front entry door you are welcomed by an impressive 2 story foyer with hardwood floors and curved staircase with custom wrought iron railings, art niches and curved walls. This bright and open home has gorgeous decorator finishes throughout with a European flair.  The family room has a wonderful built-in entertainment center with raised hearth, gas log fireplace, an atrium window picturing the surrounding mountains, a bay window to enjoy the city views and is open to the kitchen and eating nook.  A cooks delight kitchen with antiqued cabinets, tile counter tops, hardwood floor and gas downdraft range, pantry, island and breakfast bar.  Enjoy dining in the nook while looking out to the peaceful surroundings with curved French door access to back patio.   The formal dining room is separated from the kitchen by an arched doorway and features a coffered ceiling and cozy hearth room with gas log fireplace and built-ins.  There is also a library or office and a powder room on the main level.  A beautiful curved staircase brings you to the upper level which includes a master bedroom suite with cathedral ceiling, large walk-in closet and elegant 5 piece master bath, two spacious bedrooms and a full bathroom.  The walk-out basement is the perfect gathering spot for family enjoyment and fun and includes a guest bedroom with private full bathroom and the laundry room.  The spacious 3 car garage includes built-in cabinets and a work bench.  The driveway is South facing. There are views from almost every window of this home as well as an abundance of wildlife to enhance your Colorado experience.  All of the furnishings are available for sale or you can purchase it furnished for a negotiated price.

Neighborhood Description

The house has a great view.  All the neighbors are nice.
